items.title: OpenAI releases ‘largest, most knowledgable’ model GPT-4.5 with reduced hallucinations and high API price

items.title: Qodo’s open code embedding model sets new enterprise standard, beating OpenAI, Salesforce
items.description: The 1.5B-parameter Qodo-Embed-1-1.5B is available on Hugging Face under the OpenRAIL++-M license, allowing developers to integrate it freely
